            In your project you will know everybody who works for you.
            Most <a href="http://www.yegor256.com/2015/10/27/outsourcing-doesnt-work.html">outsourcing providers</a>
            will disallow you to contact their programmers directly.
            Because they <a href="http://www.yegor256.com/2015/07/21/hourly-pay-modern-slavery.html">sell people</a>.
            We don't.
            Our product is project management.
            We fully disclose contact information of all engineers working with you.
            We even allow you to work with them directly, if you wish.
            We are very confident in our
            <a href="http://www.xdsd.org">management model</a>.
